{"tid":2231031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【赴台無期】台拒讓陳同佳自由行赴台自首　評論料其短期內難起行","createTime":"2020-10-05T11:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T15:24:18.000Z","uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"443286c2eef4dc52350a08d13f64f42b1ab286d9","tid":2231031,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"管浩鳴引述台灣律師稱，需時數天處理陳同佳自首安排。台灣則稱陳同佳不能以自由行方式赴台，指港府毋須「推來推去」。港府批評台灣作政治炒作、自圓其說，重申陳同佳是自由人，政府無法干預。評論認為陳同佳案涉及兩岸關係，北京不欲台港有官方往來，相信陳同佳短期內赴台無望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=407909&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407909%26refer%3DShare&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f87a83cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407909%26refer%3DShare&h=4cd5a5d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=407909&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"ccd1ad6938e81c52d2de60ead257711eb58fffca","tid":2231031,"uid":172172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"陳同佳又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3520d4d384e035b01b9b1ff5bb77fa586200d6","tid":2231031,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d5bc793730a5dea12641ba679763a0a8af24706","tid":2231031,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"佳佳：今次唔係我唔想去喇，潘太你去屌柒777吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d947644b35455d6dc096328dd6d1e5f1e3e64401","tid":2231031,"uid":100772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:19:04.000Z","msg